videos.description: Ebuka Izundu gets the dish from Chris Lykes and throws down the easy bucket.
videos.headline: Miami's Izundu stuffs in the emphatic slam

videos.description: Miami's Chris Lykes puts the ball behind his back and lays it in though contact for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Lykes cuts to basket with nifty move for and-1 layup

videos.description: Miami's Bruce Brown Jr. gets the lob from Ja'Quan Newton and throws it down with authority in the first half.
videos.headline: Brown gets airborne for monster dunk

videos.description: Miami's Bruce Brown gets yet another lob from Ja'Quan Newton and slams it home for the Hurricanes.
videos.headline: Brown drops the hammer again
